Lelo, iwe niye hebu wawo, chino chochipetela niicho, na chino niicho chimtogole mweye.
Lelo one chipetigwa kuwa Chilisito Mkombola kazilibuka, habali wamwenga wenu wolonga kuwa wanhu wadanganike hawezazilibuka bule?
