Fana viya Bulahimu viyamuhuwile Mulungu, nayo Mulungu kamtanga kwa iyo kuwa ni yanogile haulongozi ha Mulungu."
Maabaho muvimanye kuwa wanhu waja weli na uhuwilo wawo wawo ni welesi wa Bulahimu.
Maandiko Yelile viyalongile kuwa Mulungu kezawatagusa wanhu weli siyo Wayahudi kwa ichimu cha uhuwilo, yang'hali hayakalile yolonga, kampetela Bulahimu Mbuli Inogile, viyalongile, "Kufosela weye, Mulungu kezawatemela mate wanhu wa zisi zose."
Ivo wanhu wose wowomuhuwila Mulungu wezatemiligwa mate hamwe na Bulahimu, munhu wa uhuwilo.
Wanhu wose woyotogola kutenda vinhu viya viwalondigwe na Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa, wose wokwikigwa muna yamalagilizo ya Mulungu, kwaviya Yamaandiko Yelile yolonga, "Munhu yoyose yolema kutenda chila chinhu chochandikigwe muna ichitabu cha Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa, kelagusigwa."
Lelo yowoneka kuwa habule munhu yoyose yoyowoneka kanoga haulongozi ha Mulungu kwa kuyamha Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa. Kwaviya Yamaandiko Yelile yolonga, "Munhu yanogile haulongozi ha Mulungu kezawona kwaviya kohuwila."
Mbali Malagilizo hayasang'hanigwe na uhuwilo bule, mbali Yamaandiko Yelile yolonga, "Munhu yoyotenda mbuli za Malagilizo, kezakuwa ngima kwa yayo."
Mbali Chilisito kachikombola kulawa muna ditukwa da Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa, kwaviya Mulungu kamtenda yawe tembe kwa ichimu chetu, fana Maandiko Yelile viyolonga, "Munhu yoyose yokugwa munaumsalaba kezafunigwa."
Kachilongela vino muladi mate yoyamwing'hile Bulahimu yapate kuwafikila wanhu weli siyo Wayahudi kufosela Yesu Chilisito, na muladi kwa uhuwilo chitogole Muhe Yelile yoyalaganiligwe na Mulungu.
Ndugu zangu, nolonda kulonga na mweye simwe kwa mbuli ya chila siku. Habule munhu yoyodaha kusegeza hebu kongeza chinhu chochose muna ufalume wa munhu viyakomeleze kukomeleza lagano jake. Ivo niivo viyolondeka kwa mbuli zino.
Mbuli za Mulungu zilondeka kufosela Bulahimu na lukolo lwake. Maandiko Yelile halongile, "Na lukolo," fana viyalongile wanhu wengi, mbali kalonga, "Na lukolo lwako," munhu imwe niiyo Chilisito Mulopozi.
Maabaho nolonga vino, Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa miyaka magana malongo mane na malongo mane hamwande, hadaha bule kulema lagano diya Mulungu viyakomezelile kutenda viya viyalongile, ivo yoitenda chilagano kuwa hachidaha bule.
Kwaviya one uhazi wa Mulungu ulawilila kwa ichimu cha Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Bulahimu, basi uludonho luno Mulungu kamwing'ha Bulahimu hawizalawilila kwa ichimu cha chilagano yake.
Vino Malagilizo yandikigwa kwa ichimu choni? Yandikigwa kwa ichimu cha uhasanyi, mbaka mbeyu ya Bulahimu vondayeze, ija Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Chilisito yeli na lagano. Malagilizo yayo yeng'higwe na msenga wa kuulanga kufosela kwa msenga wa kuulanga.
Mbali mpeteli si chinhu cha munhu imwe muhala, mbali Mulungu ni imwe muhala.
Vino Malagilizo yoyamwing'hile Mulungu viibishile na malagilizo yake? Hata chidogo! Kwaviya one Malagilizo yakala yodaha kuweng'ha wanhu ugima, maabaho Mulungu yaheza kuwalonga wanhu wanogile kwa kuwinza Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa.
Mbali Yamaandiko Yelile yagubika vinhu vose muna udahi wa uhasanyi, muladi chiya Mulungu chiyawalongele wanhu waja wowamtogole na kumuhuwila Yesu Chilisito, wadahe kuzihokela wanhu wowamuhuwila.
Mbaka uhuwilo uwo ung'hali haunafika, chikala chikwalungiligwa na Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa, chitagusigwa mbaka uhuwilo ugima viukalile wouzawoneka.
Ivo Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa yachilongoze mbaka Chilisito, muladi Mulungu yachilongele kuwa cha wanhu yanogile kwaviya wamuhuwila.
Mbali sambi uhuwilo wa Mulungu vondawiza, hachifosa na Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa bule.
